description: Affinor Growers Inc., a farming technology company, focuses on developing and commercializing vertical farming technologies in North America. Its vertical growing technology helps to grow crops, such as romaine lettuce and strawberries. The company was formerly known as Affinor Resources Inc. and changed its name to Affinor Growers Inc. in May 2014. Affinor Growers Inc. was incorporated in 1996 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
